translations: 插入；[计]交叉存取（interleave 的 ing 形式）

sentences.sentence: It has an interleaving distribution of mountains, forming highlands and ravines and valleys and basins.
sentences.translation: 攀枝花属于高山和峡谷地貌，高山，峡谷和盆地夹杂其中。

sentences.sentence: The sawtooth nature of this section is again because of the interleaving of the GC and application to preserve low pause times.
sentences.translation: 造成此段呈锯齿状的原因同样是因为 GC 和应用程序交错执行以便保持低暂停时间。

sentences.sentence: CLI LOB streaming and data interleaving are not supported with Informix server because the server does not support Dynamic data Format.
sentences.translation: CLI lob流式和数据交织不受Informix服务器支持，因为服务器不支持动态数据格式。
